text: Joris Loefs (born 18 April 1973) is a Dutch rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Netherlands Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Breda
